text: Sebastian Dahlström (born 5 November 1996) is a Finnish football player currently playing for Moldovan National Division side Sheriff Tiraspol. ==Career== ===Club=== On 18 December 2019, Sheriff Tiraspol announced that Dahlström would join the club on 20 January 2020. ===International=== Dahlström made his debut for the Finland national football team on 8 January 2019 in a friendly against
